snippet.title: Chapeau Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Chapeau is out now on Steam and Nintendo Switch! 

Check it out on Steam! : https://store.steampowered.com/app/1139880/Chapeau/ 
and the Nintendo eShop! 

🎩 Party Hats Go Head to Head! 👒 Bounce, float and zoom through the air in this frantic party game, and bring back memories from the good old days of couch co-op or beat the bots in solo challenge mode.

Keep up to date by following us on: https://twitter.com/chapeauGame
Join the discord for more discussion: https://discord.gg/KUaZkte

Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/chapeau.game/
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/ChapeauGame/
